Sleeping beauty gene list from Moriarty et al.

sleepingbeauty.Rd

A Sleeping Beauty forward genetic screen identifies new genes and pathways driving osteosarcoma development and metastasis.

sleepingbeauty

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 372 rows and 7 columns.

Source

https://dx.doi.org/10.1038/ng.3293

Details

This contains rows appended from Supplementary tables 1-3.
